node.text: As RaR 3.0 nears completion we are looking to train a new group of folks to assist our current front of the house staff. We are in need of line cooks, waitstaff, and bartenders as demand and growth continue. Work ethic and willingness to learn is all we’re asking for. No prior experience necessary for any position. We’ll train the right smiling face 😃 Full-time and part-time positions available. Comment or DM us to setup an interview with management 🙌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by RAR Brewing in RAR Brewing.

node.text: All (6) flavors available in cans today for walk-up sales in our cannery garage. We also have tees and a few Candy Jar & Huffy Jar sets. Thanks for another amazing day yesterday everyone 🙏😘🎃

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by RAR Brewing in RAR Brewing.

node.text: Good morning folks!! Hope y’all had a great night! For those of you that did the late night share with us, thanks! For those that did the late late night karaoke with us, we’re sorry 🤣 Today is going to be a good one! Checkout these fresh tees 🎃🎅

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by RAR Brewing in RAR Brewing. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
*Walk-Up Limits*

Walk-Up Merch Sales:

Huffy Jars $400/set (1) Per Person
Mood Mats $35 (2) of each Per Person
Candy Jars $40/set (2) Per Person
T-Shirts $25 (No Limit)

Walk-Up Can Sales:

All OOO Flavors (2) 4-PK of each brand per person. Mixed 6-PK at (2) as well.

Presale/Walkup pickups begin tomorrow at 11am and run through next Sunday, 8/8. If this is your first trip, we conduct pickups through our cannery garage on Gay St, Saturday AND Sunday of opening weekend. The rest of the week will be through our taproom.

A quick reminder that if you are picking up more than one order to please bring our form printed and completed (if you need one shoot an email to josh@rarbrewing.com). If you can not do so our staff will gladly give you one to fill out while in-line before opening. Staff will come to you, so don’t stress. If you have your form filled out already, please submit these to josh@rarbrewing.com 🙏 A REMINDER THAT THESE BEERS NEED TO STAY COLD ALWAYS! DO NOT LET THESE GET ANYWHERE CLOSE TO WARM! 

Please try your best to keep the line straight, and organized tomorrow. We ask that you do not crowd the checkout tables once at the garage. Double check your orders once received to make sure everything is correct, and then load up before enjoying a Chessie Burger indoor OR outdoors. The street in front of RaR will be closed tomorrow 😬

We ask that you kindly leave the front of @sunnysideoftheshore shop open (there will be signage) ☀️ We do not condone the use of chairs as placeholders in line. We completely understand using them during inclement weather as you wait in shelter. With that being said, we cannot regulate public sidewalks. We also ask that you use the parking lot behind RAR or the public parking behind Chesapeake College, and not the private lot adjacent to our cannery 😄

node.text: @huffyglass sent us some more hand-blown goodies this month. We have (7) of these sets up for grabs tomorrow. Otis on top, RaR bottom. All jars come with gaskets. $400/set beginning tomorrow at 11am. OOO release details to follow later this afternoon. Tons of new merch along with walk-up OOO will be available.
